This question recalls the scene in the Odyssey,
where the shade of Agamemnon appears to Ulysses and asks for
Orestes.  Book XI. in Chapman's translation, line 603: --
..TEXT:
<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
       "Doth my son yet survive
     In Orchomen or Pylos?  Or doth live
     In Sparta with his uncle?  Yet I see
     Divine Orestes is not here with me."
